data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Short Sale. PRE-FORECLOSURE & SHORT SALE.  WHAT A GREAT OPPORTUNITY TO OWN YOUR VERY OWN POOL HOME!!  Welcome Home! Walk through the Screened-In Front Porch and into this Open Concept, Split Plan 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 2 car garage POOL HOME!  Inside Laundry, Double pane windows, Large Central Kitchen, Living Room, Family Room, Dining Room AND Dinette!  Large rear Screened-In Porch leads out to your VERY OWN Back Yard Swimming Pool Oasis, which has been maintained weekly and fully surrounded by a wooden privacy fence!  This special home with SO much potential is just WAITING for you to add your own personal touches!  **POOL HAS BEEN CONTINUOUSLY MAINTAINED WEEKLY.  -'Rheem Classic' Air Handler June 2006,  -Septic pumped 2022,   -'Whirlpool Energy Smart' Water Heater July 2011,  -Newer 'MaxFloXL15' Pool PumpMay 2021,  The Bow Window on the front of the house is damaged (see photos). We have multiple repair quotes, from both Licensed General Contractors and Handymen, for your convenience!  We are unaware of the age/condition of the roof, but we believe it to be over 15 years old.  Garbage disposal non-operational, Sprinkler system may not work.  **HOME BEING SOLD AS-IS CASH SALE ONLY. BUYER MUST PHYSICALLY SEE THE HOME AND DO THEIR OWN INSPECTIONS PRIOR TO SUBMITTING AN OFFER. ZERO DAY INSPECTION PERIOD. SELLER TO DO NO REPAIRS. MINIMUM NON-REFUNDABLE DEPOSIT OF $2,500.  **ALL INFORMATION AND MEASUREMENTS ARE DEEMED TO BE TRUE AND CORRECT, BUT THE BUYER MUST VERIFY FOR THEIR OWN INFORMATION.
